---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout navTitle="幽影櫻的MC伺服器[youer]">

<main style="
        background-image: url('Minecraft Screenshot 2025.06.26 - 01.23.07.95.png');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        height: 50vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        color: white;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    ">
    <!-- 標題文字 -->
    <div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 50px;">
        歡迎來到
    </div>
    <div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 50px;">
        幽影櫻的MC伺服器[youer]
    </div>
</main>

<div>
    &nbsp;
</div>

<div class="block">
        <!-- 伺服器位置 -->

    <div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px; text-align: center;">
        伺服器地址:
    </div>

    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-top: 20px;">
        <div style="background-color: #1e1e1e; color: #ffffff; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 8px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 18px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; ">

            <!-- 顯示伺服器地址 -->
            <div id="server-address" style="user-select: text;">mcserver.barian.ayn.moe:24565</div>

            <!-- 複製按鈕 -->
            <button onclick="copyAddress()"
                    style="background-color: #333; color: white; border: none; padding: 5px 12px; font-size: 14px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; width:4em ">
                複製
            </button>


        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function copyAddress() {
            const text = document.getElementById("server-address").innerText;
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(() => {
                alert("已複製伺服器地址！");
            });
        }
    </script>
</div>

<div class="block"><!-- 主要內容 -->
    <!-- 原本的內容貼在這裡 -->





    <div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px; text-align: center;">
        伺服器介紹
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; font-size: 20px;">
        本伺服器由幽影櫻創立，以paper伺服器中的第三世界(ncworld)為基礎創建，<br>新增了neoforge模組增加遊戲玩法，需使用nneoforger1.21.1登入
    </div>
</div>

<div class="block"><!-- 主要內容 -->
    <div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px; text-align: center;">
        世界介紹
    </div>

    <div class="album py-5 bg-body-tertiary">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-md-3 g-3">

                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm">
                        <img src="Minecraft Screenshot 2025.06.26 - 13.50.00.51.png" aria-label="Placeholder: Thumbnail" class="bd-placeholder-img card-img-top" height="225"
                              role="img" width="100%">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <strong>主世界</strong>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card-body">
                            <p class="card-text">
                                出生點位於一個盆地旁<br>
                                四周由長滿櫻花的山巒環繞<br>
                                為新開設的養老世界<br>
                                為服主目前主要活動的世界
                            </p>
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                <div class="btn-group">
                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">死亡不掉落</button>
                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">難度:普通</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm">
                        <img src="Base Profile Screenshot 2025.07.08 - 04.02.48.66.png" aria-label="Placeholder: Thumbnail" class="bd-placeholder-img card-img-top" height="225"
                              role="img" width="100%">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <strong>天堂aether(模組維度)</strong>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card-body">
                            <p class="card-text">
                                眾所周知的老牌模組aether[天境]<br>
                                使用螢石搭建傳送門框架(與地獄門雷同)<br>
                                使用水桶右鍵框架啟動傳送門<br>
                                <i>"來自地獄的螢石 怎麼可能點亮通往天堂的大門..."</i><br>
                            </p>
                            <div class="btn-group">
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">死亡不掉落</button>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">難度:普通</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm">
                        <img src="Base Profile Screenshot 2025.07.08 - 04.04.28.28.png" aria-label="Placeholder: Thumbnail" class="bd-placeholder-img card-img-top" height="225"
                              role="img" width="100%">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <strong>暮色森林(模組維度)</strong>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card-body">
                            <p class="card-text">
                                一個被永恆之夜壟罩的森林世界<br>
                                有許多新的內容可以探索<br>
                                做一個2x2的小水池，水池邊方滿植物<br>
                                為投入一顆鑽石，只見一到閃電劈過<br>通往暮色森林的傳送門就會打開
                            </p>
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                <div class="btn-group">
                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">死亡不掉落</button>
                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">難度:普通</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

</Layout>

<style>
.album.bg-body-tertiary {
    background-color: transparent !important;
}
</style>
